               <p>The witnesses were examined apart, at the request of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17710911-40-person401">
                  Mary
                   Isaacs
               <interp inst="t17710911-40-person401" type="surname" value="Isaacs"></interp>
